Package: glasstabs
Title: Animated Glass-Style Tabs and Multi-Select Filter for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Name", , "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides animated glass-morphism tab navigation and a custom
    multi-select dropdown filter widget for use in Shiny applications and
    bs4Dash dashboards. Includes three checkbox indicator styles
    (check-only, box, filled-colour), live search, select-all, and smart
    trigger labels.
